{"tid":259170,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"旅行傷感情","createTime":"2017-05-26T16:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T20:11:13.000Z","uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bb86c93b6285d194a659327c44b555f9d04fc322","tid":259170,"uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:21:55.000Z","msg":"同一男一女去旅行 本身都friend 平時係香港三個人一齊去玩都冇乜野 一去旅行就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我好似同左對情侶去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  做左佢地電燈膽咁 第一日都好地地 三個一齊行有講有笑 第二日就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢地成日一齊行 自己傾 又唔講我知 攬頭攬頸 自己兩個係到笑 我就好似跟班咁係後面唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以我都靜左 少講左好多野 佢地又問我係咪發脾氣唔開心 我咪笑笑口咁話冇囉 但知唔知我幾難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  前日佢地冇啦啦嗌交 咪痴番我 同我傾計 過左一陣好番又繼續dum底我 真係多謝哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實好想同佢地講話 不如分開玩 我諗佢地冇左我可能開心好多 但佢地一定又會話我發脾氣 又點點點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解去個旅行都咁麻煩 點解係香港冇呢d問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唉又唔話得咁多既 佢地都會同我一齊行既 可能講緊一日有一個鐘咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有兩三日 我仲捱得住 有朋友忍得到咪忍下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1169f168babcd164d7716f5f7d4a696a351b8d","tid":259170,"uid":14440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"識唔識隔行？"},{"pid":"34a4e6a3c1b7824ec4d9963ebf300f61627048fd","tid":259170,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"我同囡囡同fd三個去旅行都冇呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2bd8ea1d352f424f3aa022d335cc2c312bf31e","tid":259170,"uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識唔識隔行？</blockquote><br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc46313dfe9b46d5f575b4445db40e9c21effba","tid":259170,"uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同囡囡同fd三個去旅行都冇呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要發生係我身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dbae7bc0f44274bccfd5fdbfb1b93dcd444828","tid":259170,"uid":69791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e11e1b25c7aa8743a390f63ac0cf42f48779c2f2","tid":259170,"uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁surely佢地唔當你係朋友囉<br />\n係真朋友既話就應該要顧及朋友既感受<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n你話係香港相處時又無事<br />\n咁係咪姐係佢地去旅行嗰陣特別岩傾咋？</blockquote><br />\n可能係既 但有時真係好難受 唉都冇計啦 依加係佢地眼中我好似變左最難相處既旅伴 因為我冇同佢地一齊講一齊笑 好安靜 但有冇諗過我係因為你地個先咁靜啊 插都插唔到嘴 我可以點啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b67b9dcf8aeacee28c7db724be9ac1f8100f99","tid":259170,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"又話依家好幸福嘅"},{"pid":"be61bb858bfd5ab6fdd6cd84ee42c875f8f9cb2c","tid":259170,"uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b67b9dcf8aeacee28c7db724be9ac1f8100f99","tid":259170,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"又話依家好幸福嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"唔幸福了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩推番上黎"},{"pid":"462e2a7e3097a35d99bf26d3d53b06525ab12200","tid":259170,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be61bb858bfd5ab6fdd6cd84ee42c875f8f9cb2c","tid":259170,"uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b67b9dcf8aeacee28c7db724be9ac1f8100f99","tid":259170,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16: